::Battera::

She could see that she wasn't wanted here. "Well, if you will pardon 
me, I'll take my leave."  She stretched her wings.  "I'll bother you 
no more."  
She let go of the branch and flew off.  She tried to gain as much 
altititude before they could draw thier weapons.
